							"raw": "{\n    \"transfer_to_category_id\": \"{{transfer_category_id}}\"\n}"
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/categories/{{category_id}}",
							"host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
							"path": ["api", "categories", "{{category_id}}"]
						},
						"description": "Delete a category and transfer all its transactions to another category.\n\nRequired:\n- transfer_to_category_id: Must be same type (income→income, expense→expense)\n\nBefore using:\n1. Create/identify target category\n2. Set {{transfer_category_id}} variable with target ID\n3. Run this request"
